Jezioro  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Markusy, within Elbląg County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  north of Markusy,  south-west of Elbląg, and  north-west of the regional capital Olsztyn.
